48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"工都無返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到公司門口 唔想返<br />\n漫無目的周圍走"},{"pid":"c0a07482ea40331283af051b4045b5d741004367","tid":174481,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:10:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工都無返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到公司門口 唔想返<br />\n漫無目的周圍走</blockquote><br />\n生活始終係要過 個世界唔會停低等你<br />\n你同我都要繼續向前行<br />\n總有一日你會搵到你既最愛"},{"pid":"b41434449b064c065c78b2c37f924a0fe6ece405","tid":174481,"uid":61648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:10:59.000Z","msg":"好想再為佢做啲咩 但我連打比佢既資格都無左啦"},{"pid":"b511ca7cc8f5cf39c604d21c7d05492201e6fa89","tid":174481,"uid":61648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:11:20.000Z","msg":"不斷睇佢ig有無更新"},{"pid":"36322c0b11cad51e3e5399b93bb9bec8b21667bc","tid":174481,"uid":91104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:11:25.000Z","msg":"琴晚分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef3839e4fba45391e15ff54293066006f24dfcb","tid":174481,"uid":61648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:12:18.000Z","msg":"好痛 不過如果再揀過<br />\n我都會再同佢一齊"},{"pid":"6d70db7a43a3da63d3fecd450518cdf902e9c8c0","tid":174481,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想再為佢做啲咩 但我連打比佢既資格都無左啦</blockquote><br />\n唔好再諗住幫佢做乜野 分左手就係分左手<br />\n除左你派帽 如果唔係 你冇欠佢任何野<br />\n唔好將佢無限放大"},{"pid":"04b968f0168dd6118e1d32d132d20e2bfd063b8e","tid":174481,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>琴晚分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有手分 叻喇 想點幫你"},{"pid":"468a1024ea07acf7e12dee9b2fc2466